# Apocentro requires cross-origin isolation (SharedArrayBuffer / wasm crypto):
# without these headers, account creation and encryption fail (the app bounces
# back to /login). Hosts that support a _headers file — Cloudflare Pages,
# Netlify — will serve these. GitHub Pages CANNOT set custom headers, so it
# does NOT work for Apocentro.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
